Estavis AG Buys Divisions From Colonia Real Estate AG

-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 
2011-05-12T17:23:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/estavis-ag-buys-divisions-from-colonia-real-estate-ag.html
Estavis AG is acquiring the property
privatization division of  Colonia Real Estate AG (KBU)  as well as its
property subsidiary Colonia Residential Sales GmbH, Estavis said
in a statement today.  Estavis, a Berlin-based real estate investment company,
said Colonia’s Accentro property privatization division’s order
book has a sales value of about 350 million euros.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in  Frankfurt  at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net . 